text: Tendai Maruma (born 24 September 1992) is a Zimbabwean first-class cricketer. He was included in Zimbabwe's squad for the 2016 Africa T20 Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Zimbabwean cricketers Category:Southern Rocks cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Harare
